title: Exit to error: SDL: Can't set pallet
content:
I was playing my copy of keen4 on windows 98 and the scrolling was giving me a head ache, since I dont have internet on that computer I downloaded DosBox onto a disc and installed in on windows 98. But every time I start Commander keen I get the message:
"error, could not load color pallete."
I searched for help on this but couldn't find any thing, I hope this hasn't been asked before.
Thanks for any help.
